  "id": "xIF7nCgD",
  "slug": "platforms",
  "title": "Platforms",
  "description": "Make decks, bridges, mineshafts or even wooden coasters",
  "body": "<center>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/xIF7nCgD/images/fdd434822459aa7ff392d9640250c8b30a68b847.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"610\" height=\"105\" /></p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/xIF7nCgD/images/a986966a591c94cd19dfc079cdd7a874e8695ba1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"110\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">***&nbsp;<a style=\"color: #ff6600;\" href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/shetiphiancore\" rel=\"nofollow\">ShetiPhianCore</a> Required! ***</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Build&nbsp;decks, bridges, roofs, mine shafts, or even wooden coasters.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Combine nearly any 2 blocks or items (modded or vanilla).</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">If one block used emits light the crafted item will as well.</span></p>\n\n<details>\n<summary>Click for Wrench help</summary>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Recipe</strong></h3>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/xIF7nCgD/images/c0e69e6902cc1ce1bc8ae9bb18d8c3417d2a094b.png\" width=\"250\" height=\"116\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Main-Hand</strong></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">(right-click) rotate.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">(shift-right-click) change between similar styles. If there is alot a GUI opens.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Use off-hand \"Selection GUI\" for more control.</p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://imgur.com/972tnYk.gif\" width=\"400\" height=\"221\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Off-Hand</strong></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Wrench in Off-Hand and Main-Hand holding item from this mod.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Displays placement ghost.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">(right-click) On similar block extends placement.</p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://imgur.com/6W7ubI1.gif\" width=\"400\" height=\"221\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Selection GUI</strong></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Wrench in Off-Hand and Main-Hand empty.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">(right-click) start selection box. (right-click) again to confirm selection and open \"Selection GUI\".</p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://imgur.com/BDheMOW.gif\" width=\"400\" height=\"221\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Add/Remove/Replace</strong></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Open the \"Selection GUI\" like before.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">use the + or - buttons to quickly build.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Settings are copied from the first block selected.</p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://imgur.com/v2qHK3a.gif\" width=\"400\" height=\"221\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n</details>\n\n<details>\n<summary>Click for Platformer help</summary>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Recipe</strong></h3>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/xIF7nCgD/images/9ee84504089617c5f99ae98eecfb0ca09e35d85e.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"142\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>UI</strong></h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Place 2 blocks in the slots on the left. Pick a style and pull them from the UI.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Blocks must be in the bottom row in the UI to craft.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Deconstructing is possible. You must put in 2 or 4 minimum depending on output.</p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://imgur.com/9N8r6ZA.gif\" width=\"400\" height=\"221\" /></p>\n</details>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/xIF7nCgD/images/843885170c0263133ed605d0992e0ae4811d7a52.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"75\" /></p>\n<p><span><font size=6><strong>Frames, Floors &amp; Platforms</strong></font></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Frames can have soul/redstone/torches applied to them.</span></p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/xIF7nCgD/images/0bc36a294d400667847e12d4c0a6d7b94cbf4f78.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"616\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/xIF7nCgD/images/843885170c0263133ed605d0992e0ae4811d7a52.png\" width=\"640\" height=\"75\" /></p>\n<p><span><font size=6><strong>Ramps, Steps &amp; Stairs</strong></font></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">-</span></p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/xIF7nCgD/images/4f525accd4f0fcf4f1dbc372f6887f9bd16380c1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"360\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/xIF7nCgD/images/843885170c0263133ed605d0992e0ae4811d7a52.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"75\" /></p>\n<p><span><font size=6><strong>Hand Rails &amp; Rises</strong></font></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">-</span></p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/xIF7nCgD/images/4595bd002e5ec00adeb231972ee2b2f9703b3ef9.png\" width=\"650\" height=\"474\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/xIF7nCgD/images/843885170c0263133ed605d0992e0ae4811d7a52.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"75\" /></p>\n<p><span><font size=6><strong>Roofs</strong></font></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">When a \"rise\" or \"handrail\" is placed on a roof they become a chimney or pipe.</span></p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/xIF7nCgD/images/938bf671e14bed6603c53d97d1629084d8046f92.png\" width=\"650\" height=\"450\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/xIF7nCgD/images/843885170c0263133ed605d0992e0ae4811d7a52.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"75\" /></p>\n<p><span><font size=6><strong>Tools</strong></font></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">The Wrench is a very important tool. Try it in your off-hand.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">The Platformer is used to craft everything else from the mod.</span></p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/xIF7nCgD/images/eb7037d541c8cbc147c41570f06fcf8aae1b5844.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"484\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/xIF7nCgD/images/843885170c0263133ed605d0992e0ae4811d7a52.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"75\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Carpet can be placed on platforms.</span></p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://imgur.com/8KRXg7D.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"359\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Snow or Sand will accumulate in their respective biomes.</span></p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://imgur.com/Wim30TB.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"359\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Chimneys &amp; Pipes emit particles (toggle-able).</span></p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://imgur.com/MJ4o4eh.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"359\"></p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/xIF7nCgD/images/843885170c0263133ed605d0992e0ae4811d7a52.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"75\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Submit localization files on <a href=\"https://github.com/ShetiPhian/Localizations-and-Issues\">github</a>.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Found a bug?, use the <a href=\"https://github.com/ShetiPhian/Localizations-and-Issues/issues\">Issue Tracker</a>.</strong></p>\n</center>",
